-- Namdeb, De Beers Unit in Namibia,Is  Facing a Strike Over Wages on July 12
-- Chamwe Kaira
-- 2010-07-08T07:46:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/namdeb-de-beers-unit-in-namibia-is-facing-a-strike-over-wages-on-july-12.html

          
          
             Workers at Namdeb, the diamond-mining
joint venture between Namibia and De Beers, voted to strike on
July 12 over wages, Polivester Hangula, a spokesman for the
Mineworkers Union of Namibia, said in a phone interview today
from Oranjemund.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
